{"ts":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-o1c53b"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Sentry PM-CLI-2D: storage-integrity history scan reads .jsonl directories as files"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"A production Sentry event from pm merge reconcile shows scanHistoryStreams throwing EISDIR when the history directory contains an entry named with a .jsonl suffix that is itself a directory. Harden the SDK storage-integrity primitive so hostile, malformed, or concurrently changing directory entries become structured integrity findings instead of crashing validation."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:history","area:sdk","area:validation","observability","sentry","storage-integrity"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"A .jsonl-named directory cannot crash scanStorageIntegrity; the malformed entry is reported with a stable tracker-relative path and actionable detail; normal history streams remain unchanged; focused and full 100% coverage gates pass; the live Sentry issue is resolved only after exact-head proof."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-o2kc"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/environment","value":"production"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Create a directory at .agents/pm/history/example.jsonl, then run pm validate --check-storage-integrity or pm merge reconcile."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Storage-integrity validation completes deterministically and reports the non-regular history entry as an integrity finding without throwing."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"scanHistoryStreams calls readFile on the directory and throws EISDIR, aborting merge reconciliation and blocking the Sentry release gate."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/affected_version","value":"2026.7.20"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"sdk/governance/storage-integrity"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/regression","value":true},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-7o0s","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z"},{"id":"pm-mfkv92","kind":"discovered_from","created_at":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z"},{"id":"pm-p5u6","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-21T11:15:57.325Z","author":"codex-root","text":"text=Duplicate check: searched all tracker statuses for PM-CLI-2D, EISDIR, scanHistoryStreams, illegal directory reads, and storage-integrity directory entries. No canonical item covers this exact failure; pm-mfkv92 is the merge-reconcile origin, pm-7o0s is prior disappearing-stream resilience, and pm-p5u6 owns release observability. Live evidence: Sentry PM-CLI-2D event 0705cf2439944c5f88ee0c2068c4add5 at 2026-07-21T07:29:28Z."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"39ff2b84b1a57d0baff97f581328d75bc1f0b95bbae22b05fac8df6242984359","message":"Track live Sentry storage-integrity crash with all-status duplicate evidence"}
